    <li><strong>Cost Efficiency:</strong> Centrifuges eliminate the ongoing expense of filter media, reduce labor costs through automatic operation, and minimize waste oil disposal volumes by recovering usable oil.</li>
    <li><strong>Versatile Options:</strong> Multiple centrifuge models from 10 GPM to 50+ GPM accommodate everything from small re-refining operations to large-scale commercial waste oil processing.</li>
    <li><strong>Automation:</strong> Self-cleaning centrifuges operate continuously with <a href="/industrial-centrifuge-controls/">PLC-based controls</a> managing sludge ejection cycles, feed rates, and process monitoring &mdash; minimal operator oversight required.</li>
  </ul>

